# 301 Redirects Configuration
# This file shows example redirect rules for expired domains or URL changes
# 
# Format: old-path    new-path    301
# 
# Examples:

# Redirect old expired domain to new site
# https://oldcompliancesite.com/*  https://demo.example.com/:splat  301

# Redirect old service pages to new structure
/old-services/dot-number  /services/new-usdot.html  301
/old-services/boc3  /services/boc-3.html  301
/register  /services/new-usdot.html  301
/contact-us  /#contact  301

# Redirect HTTP to HTTPS (if not handled by server)
# http://demo.example.com/*  https://demo.example.com/:splat  301

# Redirect www to non-www (or vice versa, choose one)
# https://www.demo.example.com/*  https://demo.example.com/:splat  301